{"title":"民歌","authors":["江东池"],"dates":[{"year":1949,"month":12,"day":4}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"民歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"江东池"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一、"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小小子，不淘气，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妈妈给俺织花布"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妈妈说："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"花布织一丈"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"给俺小小做衣裳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白布织一匹"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"给哥哥他们做军衣。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小小子，不淘气，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爸爸给俺养种地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爸爸说："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"粮打九石九"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"买头大黄牛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"粮打十石三"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"公粮送到长江南。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二、"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红红枣，黄黄梨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"树棵底下坐着个小闺女，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"头不抬，手不闲"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"花花手巾绣牡丹"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"牡丹花，好新鲜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"旁边字儿一串串，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"针针倒，倒倒针，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绣块手巾送亲人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要问亲人是那个？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"上绣：“人民解放军。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三、"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"公鸡打鸣咯咯＠"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"俺家有了房子有了地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"政府叫俺好好生产"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爸说：“过好了给俺娶媳妇。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黎鸡打翅"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爸爸妈妈下地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奶奶做饭蒸饼子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"姐姐纺个穗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"嫂嫂织花布"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妈妈叫我好好念书，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“大了，给老百姓办事。”"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":5,"page_end":5}